<HEAD>Soviet Authorities Expel Five Estonians</HEAD>
<DATELINE>STOCKHOLM, Sweden (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   An Estonian nationalist, his family and
the wife of another nationalist were kicked out of the Soviet Union
on Saturday, according to a spokesman for a Stockholm-based
Estonian nationalist organization.
   Mart Kikerpuu, spokesman for Hjalpcentralen, an organization
